name: Satfi
description: Satfi is a fractionalized piece of a bitcoin. The Bitcoin price has been ranging around $100,000 recently. Satfi wants to help push it higher. Paired with wbtc as the primary lp, the higher the token goes, the more wbtc gets sucked into the pool. Let's eat up that supply! Launched at $100K market cap with 100M supply Every pump absorbs more wBTC into the liquidity pool. Total supply equals the number of satoshis in 1 Bitcoin, creating a symbolic connection between $SATFI and Bitcoin's smallest unit.
